<%- include("partials/header", { title: title }) %>

<main>
  <h2>Service Project: Salsa Growing Kit</h2>

  <section class="card">
    <h3>Step 1: Gather Materials</h3>
    <img src="/images/dirt.jpg" alt="Soil used for planting">
    <img src="/images/toilet-roll.jpg" alt="Toilet paper rolls used as seed starter cups">
    <p>
      We use simple materials like soil and recycled toilet paper rolls to create seed starter cups.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h3>Step 2: Plant Ingredients</h3>
    <img src="/images/tomato-plant.jpg" alt="Tomato plant growing">
    <img src="/images/pepper.jpg" alt="Pepper plant">
    <img src="/images/cilantro.jpg" alt="Cilantro plant">
    <p>
      The salsa kit includes tomatoes, peppers, and cilantro — key ingredients for fresh salsa.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h3>Step 3: Harvest Ingredients</h3>
    <img src="/images/garlic-onion.jpg" alt="Garlic and onion for salsa">
    <img src="/images/salsa-parts.jpg" alt="Salsa ingredients prepared">
    <p>
      Once grown, ingredients can be combined with garlic and onion to prepare salsa.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h3>Step 4: Enjoy the Result</h3>
    <img src="/images/salsa.jpg" alt="Fresh homemade salsa">
    <img src="/images/salsa-jar.jpg" alt="Salsa stored in a jar">
    <p>
      The final result is fresh, homemade salsa created from ingredients grown at home.
    </p>
  </section>
</main>

